
Requirenets for control machine:
Python 2.6 installed
OS: Red Hat, Debian, CentOS, OS X, any of the BSDs, and so on.


For managed nodes:
On the managed nodes, you only need Python 2.4 or later, but if you are running less than Python 2.5 on the remotes, 
you will also need:  python-simplejson


Install on control machine:
sudo apt-get install python-setuptools
sudo easy_install pip
sudo pip install paramiko PyYAML jinja2 httplib2 markupsafe
sudo apt-get install python-dev
sudo pip install ansible

Link: http://www.hashbangcode.com/blog/ansible-automation-engine

